headline: 3 Top ETFs I Plan to Buy in May for Passive Income
summary: The JPMorgan Nasdaq: Equity Premium ETF generates income from writing call options.  My strategy is to grow my passive income so that it can cover my basic living expenses.  Three of my favorites are Schwab U.S. Dividend Equity ETF (NYSEMKT: SCHD), JPMorgan Nasdaq Equity Premium Income ETF (NASDAQ: JEPQ), and Vanguard Total Bond Market ETF (NASDAQ: BND).
